"<h1>頁面源代碼</h1>\n\n<div class=\"page-source\">\n\t[[include <a href=\"http://scp-zh-tr.wikidot.com/theme:paperstack\">:scp-zh-tr:theme:paperstack</a>]]<br />\n[[include <a href=\"http://scp-zh-tr.wikidot.com/component:toggle-sidebar\">:scp-zh-tr:component:toggle-sidebar</a>]]<br />\n<br />\n[[a href=&quot;/&quot; id=&quot;header-link&quot;]]<br />\n[[/a]]<br />\n[[a href=&quot;#side-bar&quot; id=&quot;sb-button&quot;]]<br />\n≡<br />\n[[/a]]<br />\n<br />\n[[include <a href=\"/info:start\">info:start</a>]]<br />\n[[=]]<br />\n**原文：**[https://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/curated-tale-series CURATED TALE SERIES]<br />\n由[[*user EstrellaYoshte]]編寫，以及[[*user Oboebandgeek99]]、[[*user TopDownUnder]]、[[*user JakdragonX]]、[[*user Yossipossi]]、[[*user HarryBlank]]的貢獻 <br />\n[[/=]]<br />\n[[include <a href=\"/info:end\">info:end</a>]]<br />\n<br />\n[[div class=&quot;bigtitle&quot;]]<br />\n+ 推薦故事系列<br />\n[[/div]]<br />\n<br />\n+ 當月展出<br />\n<br />\n[[div class=&quot;display-container&quot;]]<br />\n[[div class=&quot;tale-cover&quot;]]<br />\n[[image https://i.imgur.com/y95grG2.png link=&quot;https://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/speed-demon-hub&quot;]]<br />\n[[/div]]<br />\n[[div class=&quot;tale-desc&quot;]]<br />\n+ Speed Demon<br />\n++++ 由[[[dr-arvind-desais-personnel-file|A Random Day]]]所著<br />\n<br />\n//The first rule of witches — they're all bitches.//<br />\n<br />\nRukmini &quot;the Rookie&quot; Mahakali是Chicago Specter的核心。她是個名符其實的鬼靈，將死亡的惡魔注入自己的身軀，以在充滿罪犯的裏世界中製造混亂。她身體裡的魔法心臟是她的秘密，那是在熱情的拌嘴中從她前女友的胸膛裡偷出來的。<br />\n<br />\n所以當the Rookie的前女友闖入她的新空間來取回它時，讓血液可以流過全身變成她最不嚴重的煩惱了。<br />\n<br />\n++++ (Description by [[[uraniumempire|UraniumEmpire]]])<br />\n[[/div]]<br />\n[[/div]]<br />\n<br />\n[!-- <br />\n+ Conwell的選擇<br />\n<br />\n[[div class=&quot;display-container second&quot;]]<br />\n[[div class=&quot;tale-cover&quot;]]<br />\n[[image /florence-thorne-hub/PNM_3.png link=&quot;https://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/florence-thorne-hub&quot;]]<br />\n[[/div]]<br />\n[[div class=&quot;tale-desc&quot;]]<br />\n+ The Phoenix, The Nightingale, and The Magpies<br />\n++++ 由[[[greenwolf-s-author-page|GreenWolf]]]著作<br />\n<br />\n//The SCP Foundation has captured one of the most powerful mages ever born. The question remains: What will they do to ensure she remains on their side?//<br />\n<br />\n隨著第七次超自然戰爭降臨人間，基金會竭盡全力確保他們的舊敵人無法再次站起。唯一的方法難以想像——招募新敵人作為盟友。<br />\n<br />\n有著縱火、魔法、鵝以及背叛，//The Phoenix, The Nightingale, and The Magpies//講述對付這個不斷改變的現實的基金會最新武器——Florence Elsinger的人生與時光。<br />\n<br />\n++++ (評論：[[[ralliston-s-authorpage|Ralliston]]]和[[[researcher-conwell-s-personnel-file|Jacob Conwell]]])<br />\n[[/div]]<br />\n[[/div]]<br />\n--]<br />\n<br />\n+ 迅速崛起<br />\n[[div class=&quot;multi-grid&quot;]]<br />\n<br />\n[[div style=&quot;border-radius: 0; border solid 0.125rem rgb(183, 18, 52);&quot;]]<br />\n[[=image https://filedmns2.wdfiles.com/local--files/dokumentoz/TMOtopBar.png height=&quot;70px&quot;]]<br />\n<br />\n+ Telecommunications Monitoring Office<br />\n它的成員大部分是1級權限的部員，他們花一整天聽著電話，不斷重複。<br />\n<br />\n這是他們的故事。<br />\n<br />\n[[[telecommunications-monitoring-office-hub|She was surprised to find herself crying. Apparently that wasn't disqualifying.]]]<br />\n[[/div]]<br />\n<br />\n[[div style=&quot;border: solid 0.0625rem rgb(160,160,160); background-color:rgba(224,224,224,0.25); border-radius:0; box-shadow: none;&quot;]]<br />\n+ **The Man Who Stood Alone**<br />\n隨著基金會自聚光燈下退出，其他組織開始崛起以填上這份權力空白，卻留下大量的破壞。<br />\n<br />\n腐敗開始猖狂於各個階層間，而基金會開始分崩離析。<br />\n<br />\n[[[the-man-who-stood-alone-hub|Are you going to stand there all day? Get in.]]]<br />\n[[/div]]<br />\n<br />\n[[/div]]<br />\n<br />\n-----<br />\n<br />\n+ 社群推薦<br />\n<br />\n++ 最高人氣<br />\n[[div class=&quot;multi-grid-small&quot;]]<br />\n[[div]]<br />\n[[=image https://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/curated-tale-series/atmm.png height=&quot;70px&quot;]]<br />\n+ 逆模因部<br />\n[[[antimemetics-division-hub|不對，這不是你第一天來這裡上班。]]]<br />\n記憶易變，但這系列無法被遺忘。由qntm著作的經典基金會閱讀體驗。<br />\n[[/div]]<br />\n<br />\n[[div style=&quot;background-color:#21252E; color: #ededed;&quot;]]<br />\n[[=image https://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/black-autumn-hub/scp-halloween-alone.png height=&quot;70px&quot;]]<br />\n+ ##EB6123|Black Autumn II: Rise Of the Pit Sloth##<br />\n[[[rise-of-the-pit-sloth-hub|Soon, the lights dim, and the movie begins.]]]<br />\n威斯康辛州斯洛斯皮特裡的謠傳開始成真，而這時有一段新的故事正要進城。Site-87第二陰暗的十月成為一盞閃耀明亮的聚光燈，照亮由人物主導推動的一齣齣恐怖喜劇。<br />\n[[/div]]<br />\n<br />\n[[div class=&quot;standalone&quot;]]<br />\n[[=image https://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/curated-tale-series/starswait.png height=&quot;70px&quot;]]<br />\n+ The Stars Do Not Wait For You<br />\n[[[the-stars-do-not-wait-for-you|It's quiet out here.]]]<br />\n在萬物皆無的世界末端，一場令人難以忘懷的美麗探險，由Dmatix著作。<br />\n[[/div]]<br />\n<br />\n[[div]]<br />\n[[=image https://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/horizon-initiative-hub/sun.jpg height=&quot;70px&quot;]]<br />\n+ Et Tam Deum Petivi<br />\n[[[etdp-hub-page|Alone, the light was too weak to face the darkness.]]]<br />\n在這個有關愛情的暖心系列中，Mary-Ann及Salah對異常世界與彼此有了更多的認識。發生在宗教衝突的時代，身外與內心都是。<br />\n[[/div]]<br />\n<br />\n[[div]]<br />\n[[=image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-3448/dammerung-logo100.png height=&quot;70px&quot;]]<br />\n+ 死亡終了第一季<br />\n[[[end-of-death-hub|Life's a bitch.]]]<br />\n沒人會在世界終焉時死掉，所以世界正走向終焉，而且Joyce Michaels被捲進了其內。第一季描述她在探索自己的不死人生時的奮鬥，同時調查這個新常態是如何產生的。<br />\n[[/div]]<br />\n<br />\n[[div style=&quot;background-color: #212121;&nbsp;&nbsp;border-top: 0.2rem solid red; border-bottom: 0.2rem solid red; border-radius: 5% 10%; color: #FF3300;&quot;]]<br />\n[[=image http://smlt.wdfiles.com/local--files/plaguebearer%3Anobody/%3F height=&quot;70px&quot;]] <br />\n+ **##red|THE MAN IN THE## ###fff|WHITE## ##red|SUIT##**<br />\n[[[the-man-in-the-white-suit-hub|He knows me almost as well as I know myself.]]]<br />\n有人想要對沒有人復仇，而他會為了復仇走到天涯海角。某一方面，他的追蹤技術只能與他徹底的決心相比；另一方面，沒有人腦袋裡最大的問題的答案可能在他手裡：<br />\n<br />\n「我是誰？」<br />\n[[/div]]<br />\n[[/div]]<br />\n<br />\n++ 動作／冒險<br />\n[[div class=&quot;multi-grid-small&quot;]]<br />\n[[div style=&quot;border: solid 0.3rem #C1930B; background-color: #FFFBF0;&quot;]]<br />\n[[=image https://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/curated-tale-series/bird.png height=&quot;70px&quot;]]<br />\n+ ##C1930B|Team Bird##<br />\n[[[bird|Medila help us all.]]]<br />\n鳥類贏了。古怪、驚險而且有時會起肖，鳥類部門的冒險會將你帶往你沒看過的高度。<br />\n[[/div]]<br />\n<br />\n[[div style=&quot;border: solid 0.3rem #F7E3D6&quot;]]<br />\n[[=image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/this-page-intentionally-left-blank/43pride.png height=&quot;70px&quot;]]<br />\n+ The Time After Time Password<br />\n[[[the-time-after-time-password-hub|Your plan is authorized.]]]<br />\nSite-43的反諜報計謀帶著他們環繞地球。寫得好、有吸引力又風趣，這群個性鮮明的角色絕對會襲捲全球。<br />\n[[/div]]<br />\n<br />\n[[div style=&quot;background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(6,0,96,1) 0%, rgba(0,0,2,1) 125px, rgba(238,238,238,1) 125px) padding-box, linear-gradient(0deg, #020006, #09005E) border-box; border: 0.4rem solid transparent;&quot;]]<br />\n[[=image https://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/curated-tale-series/anast.png height=&quot;70px&quot;]]<br />\n+ ##EEEEEE|ANASTASIS##<br />\n[[[anastasis-hub|I never thought I'd see that beast again.]]]<br />\nCrocosquid回來了，比以前都更加地大及壞。為了世界的未來，基金會在巨型前線傾注全力。<br />\n[[/div]]<br />\n<br />\n[[div style=&quot;color: #EDEDED; background-color: #2F333C;&quot;]]<br />\n+ ##1EB5E8|The Adventures of Siggy and RoboMonkey##<br />\n[[[the-adventures-of-siggy-and-robomonkey-hub|&quot;Let's uh… start at the beginning, shall we?&quot;]]]<br />\n//有關一個女巫和變身者在充滿惡意的世界成長的故事，在途中面對同時巨大且熟悉的危險。//<br />\n[[/div]]<br />\n<br />\n[[div style=&quot;color: #EDEDED; background-color: #2F333C; background: url(https://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/local--files/curated-tale-series/archebg.png);&quot;]]<br />\n[[=image https://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/curated-tale-series/archeico.png height=&quot;70px&quot;]]<br />\n+ ##99bbff|Archetypicals##<br />\n[[[placeholder|&quot;Hello, Doctor McDoctorate. Your meeting is in seventy-three minutes.&quot;]]]<br />\n人生只是一篇大故事，而他們是配角的原型。對冒險、有趣點子及機械降神的粉絲來說，這篇必讀。<br />\n[[/div]]<br />\n<br />\n[[/div]]<br />\n<br />\n++ 恐怖<br />\n[[div class=&quot;multi-grid-small&quot;]]<br />\n[[div style=&quot;background-color: #1D1F20; color: #C5C9C6;&quot;]]<br />\n[[=image https://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/curated-tale-series/drkstff.png height=&quot;70px&quot;]]<br />\n+ ##C5C9C6|Dark Stuff for Sleepless Nights##<br />\n[[[dark-stuff-for-sleepless-nights|It's giving me a great reason to write weekly spooOOOOoooky stories.]]]<br />\n一篇creepypasta的選集，名譽上由Darkstuff著作。<br />\n[[/div]]<br />\n<br />\n[[div]]<br />\n[[=image https://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/slipping-away/breaker height=&quot;70px&quot;]]<br />\n+ 泛空<br />\n[[[white-space-hub|屆時你又會相信我們嗎？]]]<br />\n超現實與奇幻的奇妙組合，泛空探索了身為人類活著與死去的意義，以及其中的不和諧。<br />\n[[/div]]<br />\n<br />\n[[div]]<br />\n[[=image https://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/curated-tale-series/thaumiel.png height=&quot;70px&quot;]]<br />\n+ 雙極神計畫<br />\n[[[thaumiel|維安人員會盡快前往協助。]]]<br />\n當SCP-001變糟時會發生什麼？基金會做好了準備。<br />\n[[/div]]<br />\n<br />\n[[div class=&quot;standalone&quot;]]<br />\n+ Síobhra<br />\n[[[siobhra|This war isn't glorious.]]]<br />\n由Ihp著作的這篇緊湊謎團會讓你到結局為止都如坐針氈。<br />\n[[/div]]<br />\n<br />\n[[/div]]<br />\n<br />\n++ 驚悚／謎團<br />\n[[div class=&quot;multi-grid-small&quot;]]<br />\n[[div style=&quot;border: 2px solid black; border-radius: 0;&quot;]]<br />\n[[=image https://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/grigori-karpin-s-author-page/ProjectHeca height=&quot;70px&quot;]]<br />\n+ Hecatoncheires Cycle<br />\n[[[hecatoncheires-cycle-hub|What can we learn from our enemies?]]]<br />\n來自另一個世界且已死許久的一位訪客、一位人偶師、無人道邪教、怪物、魔法還有人類英雄在這場史詩級的動作／恐怖戲劇裡相互碰撞。<br />\n[[/div]]<br />\n<br />\n[[div style=&quot;background-image: url(&quot;https://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/curated-tale-series/background-conspiracy.jpg&quot;);&nbsp;&nbsp;background-size: cover; font-family: 'Special Elite', serif;&quot;]]<br />\n[[=image https://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/curated-tale-series/headericon-conspiracy.png height=&quot;70px&quot;]]<br />\n+ Conspiracy<br />\n[[[conspiracy|McDonnell cracked the first of his stack of novels. It would be a long flight to JFK, and the pouch meant he couldn't sleep through it.]]]<br />\n湯姆克蘭西／伊恩福萊明／勞勃·勒德倫風格的神秘間諜故事，設在80年代晚期的基金會。<br />\n[[/div]]<br />\n<br />\n[[div]]<br />\n[[=image https://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/curated-tale-series/pvice.png height=&quot;70px&quot;]]<br />\n+ Portland Vice<br />\n[[[portland-vice|You want to put a contract out on skippers? Are you insane?]]]<br />\n激動特遣隊Tau-51已經花好幾個月在三波特蘭追蹤一個異常毒品製造師了，但他們的目標總是比他們領先一步。<br />\n有了來自UIU的小小幫忙，特遣隊指揮官Damian Creed及奇蹟術師Beatrice Ross接下任務，卻發現腳印指向家鄉附近。<br />\n[[/div]]<br />\n<br />\n[[div style=&quot;background-image: url(&quot;https://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/curated-tale-series/background-new-age.svg&quot;); background-size: cover; border: 3rem #1c4156; border-style: none double; border-radius: 2rem; padding: 1rem 2rem; color: #1c4156;&quot;]]<br />\n+ New Age<br />\n[[a href=&quot;new-age-hub&quot;]]&quot;They said the D means Disposable.&quot; _<br />\n&nbsp;_<br />\n&quot;Really? Is that what they said it stands for? Heh.&quot;[[/a]]<br />\n一篇被超異常陰謀劫持的十萬字監獄驚悚故事。跟隨其中一人穿過大大小小的牢房、身體上與心理上、市民與基金會間的旅途。<br />\n[[/div]]<br />\n<br />\n[[div style=&quot;color: #ffeeee; background-color: #25171e; border: solid 0.25em #b94d7b;&quot;]]<br />\n+ ##fc0000|Misfire##<br />\n[[[misfire-hub|No one said anything. No one moved.]]]<br />\n在發現兩位基金會人員被殺害之後，Site-19的電梯內發生了衝突，造成了Carlson博士的死亡。<br />\n<br />\n基金會調查員開始拼起拼圖，將事件連結起來，直到顯露出一張充滿陰謀與騙局的蜘蛛網。<br />\n[[/div]]<br />\n<br />\n[[/div]]<br />\n<br />\n++ 角色主導<br />\n[[div class=&quot;multi-grid-small&quot;]]<br />\n[[div]]<br />\n[[=image https://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--resized-images/ascension-hub/thedance/medium.jpg height=&quot;70px&quot;]]<br />\n+ Dancing with Rachael<br />\n[[[ascension-hub|This, for obvious reasons, is a last resort.]]]<br />\nRachael攪亂了自己無法想像的渾水。這不一定對踏入其中的所有人都有效。<br />\n[[/div]]<br />\n<br />\n[[div style=&quot;background-color: #EEFFCC; color: #66574F&quot;]]<br />\n[[=image https://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/curated-tale-series/tiamd.png height=&quot;70px&quot;]]<br />\n+ ##66574F|Take It Away, My Darling##<br />\n[[[take-it-away-my-darling|My sweetheart, my… daughter.]]]<br />\nFaeowynn Wilson努力訴說她的父親、家庭、她自己，還有他留下的其他所有遺物的故事。<br />\n[[/div]]<br />\n<br />\n[[div class=&quot;standalone&quot;]]<br />\n+ Kyoufu-0<br />\n[[[kyoufu-0|The 10th Seraph of Noise has caught its prey.]]]<br />\n以引人入勝的開頭到暖心結局的驚人故事，由NatVoltiaic著作。<br />\n[[/div]]<br />\n<br />\n[[div]]<br />\n[[=image https://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/curated-tale-series/wwyddicon.png height=&quot;70px&quot;]]<br />\n+ ##662E63|When Will You Die for the Last Time in My Dreams##<br />\n[[[wwydftltimd-hub|FOUNDER VERONICA FITZROY DEAD AT 32]]]<br />\n在亂得一通的世界中，人們做著糟糕的事情、搞砸一切、做一些靈魂搜索再做更多糟糕事情，但有適當的背景音樂。<br />\n<br />\nWWYDftLTiMD將幽默、自省、角色主導的動作戲及敏感話題編織成一個混音帶型的包裹，變成了扣人心弦的故事。 <br />\n[[span class=&quot;content-warning&quot;]]虐待、血腥、誹謗、自殺、自我認同問題、同性／跨性別恐懼症[[/span]]<br />\n[[/div]]<br />\n<br />\n[[div class=&quot;standalone&quot; style=&quot;background: linear-gradient(#1A1B28, #242D35); color: #f4f4f4;&quot;]]<br />\n+ ##FF8826|Death Perception##<br />\n[[[death-perception|&quot;It felt like a memory of our mother.&quot;]]]<br />\n與好奇心旺盛的機動特遣隊「Samsara」一同踏上萬聖節冒險。他們著手寫起糟糕的同人作品、加入降神會、召喚憤怒的糟糕亡靈，也許在途中對自己更加了解。<br />\n[[/div]]<br />\n<br />\n[[div]]<br />\n[[=image https://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/curated-tale-series/likeclockwork.png height=&quot;70px&quot;]]<br />\n+ ##DD6BE5|...Like Clockwork##<br />\n[[[like-clockwork-hub|Eventually, the answer will come for why things are the way they are.]]]<br />\n跟隨塔羅蘭研究員一同探索真實與--虛假--、混沌與秩序、內部和永恆之間的分界，也許在艱難的路途中和解。<br />\n<br />\n[[span class=&quot;content-warning&quot;]]虐待、血腥、自殘、自殺、肉體恐怖[[/span]]<br />\n[[/div]]<br />\n<br />\n[[/div]]<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n++ 日常<br />\n[[div class=&quot;multi-grid-small&quot;]]<br />\n[[div style=&quot;background-color: #DCF2B0; color: #3B5C0A;&quot;]]<br />\n[[=image https://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/theme:kiryu-labs-theme/kiryulabs.png height=&quot;70px&quot;]]<br />\n+ ##6C7F41|桐生實驗室##<br />\n[[[kiryu-labs-hub|桐生實驗室一共由18個操作室組成。]]]<br />\n圍繞著一位身為心理學家的古怪實驗室主任、身為動物行為學家的首席助理死黨，還有一位喜歡刀子的特工的日常故事。還有來自一位蝴蝶生物學家以及住在休息室裡、暴躁、留了鬍子的龍的友情客串。<br />\n[[/div]]<br />\n<br />\n[[div style=&quot;background-color: #F1F5F9; color: #0E0A06; border-radius: 0; background-image: linear-gradient(to left, black, black 3px, transparent 3px), linear-gradient(to bottom, black, black 3px, transparent 3px), url(&quot;/local--files/curated-tale-series/background-flow.png&quot;), linear-gradient(to right, black, black 3px, transparent 3px); background-position: left bottom, left bottom, left bottom, left bottom; background-repeat: no-repeat, no-repeat, no-repeat, no-repeat; background-size: cover, cover, cover, cover;&quot;]]<br />\n[[=image https://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/curated-tale-series/headericon-flow.png height=&quot;140px&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: -70px;&quot;]]<br />\n+ Flow<br />\n[[[flow-hub|Most often repeated notion during creation process is a sentiment of being out of control, artists noting that their activities are guided or even straight out directed by some uncontrollable force, described very often with a term of &quot;Flow&quot;.]]]<br />\n想要了解自己能力及抓住靈感多變性的異術家們的故事。<br />\n[[/div]]<br />\n[[/div]]<br />\n<br />\n++ LGBT+<br />\n[[div class=&quot;multi-grid-small&quot;]]<br />\n[[div style=&quot;border-radius: 2.5rem&quot; class=&quot;standalone&quot;]]<br />\n[[=image https://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/curated-tale-series/pfytico.png height=&quot;70px&quot;]]<br />\n+ Penny for Your Thoughts?<br />\n[[[penny-for-your-thoughts|And plus you know it's my lucky penny]]]<br />\n古怪又可愛，//Penny for Your Thoughts?//以簡訊格式傳達友好與慰藉的合適點。<br />\n[[/div]]<br />\n<br />\n[[div class=&quot;standalone&quot;]]<br />\n+ Content Warning: This Is Still A Foundation Story, After All<br />\n[[[content-warning-this-is-still-a-foundation-story-after-all|— and it was all a matter of which corner of the Foundation you happened to find yourself in.]]]<br />\n在基金會帷幕內與跨性別經驗有關的一篇故事，由Athenodora著作。<br />\n[[span class=&quot;content-warning&quot;]]提到跨性別恐懼症[[/span]]<br />\n[[/div]]<br />\n[[/div]]<br />\n<br />\n++ 政治虛構小說<br />\n[[div class=&quot;multi-grid-small&quot;]]<br />\n[[div style=&quot;background-color: #f5f5f5; border: solid 1px black;&quot;]]<br />\n[[=image https://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/muckscape-megagrid-mayhem-hub/MuMeMa.png height=&quot;70px&quot;]]<br />\n+ MUCKSCAPE / MEGAGRID / MAYHEM<br />\n[[[muckscape-megagrid-mayhem-hub|Full of sludge, and muck, and scum.]]]<br />\n扣人心弦地描寫了一個崩潰的世界以及身在其內的人民，由Pdeantique著作。<br />\n[[/div]]<br />\n<br />\n[[div style=&quot;border-radius: 0; border: double 0.4rem #9F0A08; background-color: #EBDBC2; color: #262017;&quot;]]<br />\n+ ##9F0A08|Matryoshka##<br />\n[[[matryoshka|NEUTRALIZE SCP-1041.]]]<br />\n所有冷戰中的大玩家都動了棋子。所有人離揭露自己的手牌都只剩一個錯步之遙。<br />\n[[/div]]<br />\n<br />\n[[div style=&quot;background-color: #F4E8E8; border: solid 3px #AD275A;&quot;]]<br />\n[[=image https://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/curated-tale-series/saffsands.png height=&quot;70px&quot;]]<br />\n+ ##C70039|In Saffron Sands##<br />\n[[[saffronsands-hub|Humor is needed to make the drab worth getting through.]]]<br />\n站上了發展中力量的舞台，In Saffron Sands鑽進了異常與正常世界如何互相映射、拉扯與交錯的本質，就在印度那迅速變換的地形中。<br />\n[[/div]]<br />\n[[/div]]<br />\n<br />\n++ 搞笑<br />\n[[div class=&quot;multi-grid-small&quot;]]<br />\n[[div]]<br />\n+ Joey Fucknuts<br />\n[[[joey-fucknuts-builds-a-flying-machine|Joey liked learning, which is why he was mayor.]]]<br />\n由CadaverCommander著作，這個奇怪地感人的故事系列會讓你不停掛著微笑。<br />\n[[/div]]<br />\n<br />\n[[div]]<br />\n+ Cack Hard<br />\n[[[cack-hub |If anyone has to suffer, it's Mr. Fish.]]]<br />\n令人驚豔的電影與文學作品，完全只透過搞笑虛構作品描寫，<br />\n[[/div]]<br />\n[[/div]]<br />\n<br />\n++ 賺人熱淚<br />\n[[div class=&quot;multi-grid-small&quot;]]<br />\n[[div class=&quot;standalone&quot;]]<br />\n+ Sometimes It's Not Funny<br />\n[[[sometimes-it-s-not-funny|this isn't a time to calm down.]]]<br />\n令人無法忘懷的故事，描寫逝世、悲痛、憤怒，以及行動的代價，由Kinchtheknifeblade著作。<br />\n[[/div]]<br />\n<br />\n[[div class=&quot;standalone&quot;]]<br />\n+ My Mother's Roses<br />\n[[[my-mothers-roses|Mom was a florist, and she loved many flowers.]]]<br />\n一位男孩與他父親為了要在情人節給母親一個驚喜的一趟單純、促進思考的旅程，由JakdragonX著作。<br />\n[[/div]]<br />\n<br />\n[[div class=&quot;standalone&quot;]]<br />\n+ [[span style=&quot;background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,131,204,1) 10%, rgba(92,97,168,1) 90%); background-clip: text;-webkit-background-clip: text;color: transparent; padding: 0 1em;&quot;]]Progressive Retrograde[[/span]]<br />\n[[[progressive-retrograde|She screamed as they pulled us into the van.]]]<br />\n它因為出自CupidCon而毫無懸念地扣人心弦，而且成功地將感情擠進SCP維基上少見的題材──浪漫。<br />\n[[/div]]<br />\n[[/div]]<br />\n<br />\n++ 雜類／其他<br />\n[[div class=&quot;multi-grid-small&quot;]]<br />\n[[div]]<br />\n+ Tales of Anomalous Items<br />\n[[[ao-hub|Pick a single item from the log and make a tale about it.]]]<br />\n就算是小事物也總是會有表面看不到的東西。<br />\n[[/div]]<br />\n<br />\n[[div class=&quot;standalone&quot;]]<br />\n+ A Memorandum<br />\n[[[a-memorandum|I don't think I've told him to change the dose.]]]<br />\n網站上巧妙說故事手法的最佳例子之一，由Taffeta著作的必讀作品。<br />\n[[/div]]<br />\n<br />\n[[div class=&quot;standalone&quot;]]<br />\n+ Breaching Boredom<br />\n[[[breaching-boredom|When was the last time I felt?]]]<br />\n簡短、緊湊、有力，Doctor Fullham讓這個故事裡塞滿了後勁。<br />\n[[/div]]<br />\n[[/div]]<br />\n<br />\n@@ @@<br />\n<br />\n-----<br />\n<br />\n+ 也請見<br />\n<br />\n* [http://scp-zh-tr.wikidot.com/series-archive 系列檔案室]<br />\n* [http://scp-zh-tr.wikidot.com/user-curated-lists 用戶推薦列表]<br />\n<br />\n[!-- 注意：CSS在下方<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<